ROPEX '81 Scheduled for
Rochester, NY, Mar. 13-15
ROPEX '81 is an "open competition"
to which all exhibitors, regardless of
club affiliation or collecting interest,
have been invited to exhibit. There will
be 2,500-3,000 pages on display.
In keeping with the ROPEX custom,
each exhibit will be judged indepen-
The Rochester Philatelic Association
has announced that ROPEX '81 is
scheduled for March 13, 14, 15, 1981 at the
Americana of Rochester Hotel, 70 State
Street, Rochester, New York.
